  "description": "üöÄ GPT-5 + Veo-3 Instagram Reel Auto-Creator & Auto-Poster\n\nDescription:\nThis n8n workflow is a fully automated short-form video content engine that takes your creative idea, turns it into a cinematic video using Google Veo-3 via Wavespeed API, writes an engaging Instagram caption with GPT-5, and instantly posts it to Instagram via Postiz‚Äîall without lifting a finger.\n\nIt‚Äôs designed for content creators, social media managers, and brands who want to produce high-quality, on-brand reels at scale without manual editing or posting.\n\nWatch Step-by-step build:\nwww.youtube.com/@automatewithmarc\n\nüí° Key Features:\nüí¨ Chat-Triggered Automation (You can replace this with On Schedule trigger for automated generation) ‚Äì Start the workflow with a simple message describing your video idea.\n\nüß† GPT-5 Video Prompt Agent ‚Äì Transforms your concept into a visually rich, cinematic prompt optimized for Veo-3.\n\nüé• Veo-3 AI Video Generation ‚Äì Creates a polished short-form reel with cinematic motion, effects, and branding.\n\n‚úçÔ∏è GPT-5 Caption Writer ‚Äì Crafts an impactful, scroll-stopping caption tailored for Instagram engagement.\n\nüì§ Auto-Posting with Postiz ‚Äì Uploads and schedules (or instantly posts) your reel to Instagram without manual steps.\n\n‚è≥ Automated Progress Checking ‚Äì Wait & retry logic ensures posting only happens when the video is fully generated.\n\nüîß Tech Stack:\nGPT-5 via OpenAI API ‚Äì AI for prompt engineering & caption creation.\n\nGoogle Veo-3 (via Wavespeed API) ‚Äì Next-gen text-to-video model for short-form content.\n\nPostiz API ‚Äì Multi-platform social media posting automation.\n\nn8n ‚Äì Orchestration & automation engine.\n\nüìå Ideal Use Cases:\nInstagram Reels / TikTok Creators who want to post daily without editing.\n\nFitness, Fashion, Travel & Lifestyle Brands looking for high-quality, thematic reels.\n\nSocial Media Agencies producing client content at scale.\n\nEvent Marketers creating same-day recap videos.\n\nüõ† Setup Instructions:\nAdd your API keys for OpenAI (GPT-5), Wavespeed (Veo-3), and Postiz.\n\nConnect Postiz to your Instagram account.\n\nTrigger the workflow with a chat message describing your desired video.\n\nWatch your idea transform into a reel‚Äîfully captioned and posted automatically.\n\nüéØ Why This Workflow Stands Out:\nEnd-to-end automation from idea ‚Üí video ‚Üí caption ‚Üí Instagram post.\n\nAI-driven creative consistency for brand identity.\n\nScales your content production without hiring editors.\n\nSEO & engagement-ready captions crafted for social virality.",
